%% Deployment Process - Parallel Deployment Innovation
%% Shows how 5 agents are deployed in parallel for speed

graph TB
    START[🚀 Start Deployment] --> LOAD[⚙️ Load .env Configuration<br/>- GCP Project ID<br/>- Region<br/>- API Keys<br/>- Notion credentials]

    LOAD --> PARALLEL{💡 Deploy Specialists<br/>in Parallel}

    subgraph "Parallel Deployment (asyncio.gather)"
        PARALLEL --> D1[📦 Deploy brand-strategist<br/>Build + Push Container<br/>Set env vars<br/>Configure A2A]
        PARALLEL --> D2[📦 Deploy copywriter<br/>Build + Push Container<br/>Set env vars<br/>Configure A2A]
        PARALLEL --> D3[📦 Deploy designer<br/>Build + Push Container<br/>Set env vars<br/>Configure A2A]
        PARALLEL --> D4[📦 Deploy critic<br/>Build + Push Container<br/>Set env vars<br/>Configure A2A]
        PARALLEL --> D5[📦 Deploy project-manager<br/>Build + Push Container<br/>Set env vars + Notion<br/>Configure A2A]
    end

    D1 --> URL1[URL 1:<br/>https://brand-strategist-xxx.run.app]
    D2 --> URL2[URL 2:<br/>https://copywriter-xxx.run.app]
    D3 --> URL3[URL 3:<br/>https://designer-xxx.run.app]
    D4 --> URL4[URL 4:<br/>https://critic-xxx.run.app]
    D5 --> URL5[URL 5:<br/>https://project-manager-xxx.run.app]

    URL1 & URL2 & URL3 & URL4 & URL5 --> UPDATE[🔄 Update A2A Configuration<br/>For each service:<br/>- Extract public URL<br/>- Set PUBLIC_HOST<br/>- Set PUBLIC_PORT=443<br/>- Set PROTOCOL=https]

    UPDATE --> COLLECT[📝 Collect All URLs<br/>agent_urls = {<br/>  brand-strategist: url1,<br/>  copywriter: url2,<br/>  ...<br/>}]

    COLLECT --> SAVE[💾 Save to .env.specialists<br/>STRATEGIST_AGENT_URL=url1<br/>COPYWRITER_AGENT_URL=url2<br/>DESIGNER_AGENT_URL=url3<br/>CRITIC_AGENT_URL=url4<br/>PM_AGENT_URL=url5]

    SAVE --> ORCHESTRATOR[🎬 Deploy Orchestrator<br/>to Agent Engine<br/>with all agent URLs<br/>in env vars]

    ORCHESTRATOR --> TEST[✅ Test Complete System<br/>python test_orchestrator.py]

    TEST --> COMPLETE[🎉 Deployment Complete!]

    subgraph "⏱️ Performance Comparison"
        SEQ[❌ Sequential Deployment:<br/>5 agents × 3 min each<br/>= ~15 minutes]

        PAR[✅ Parallel Deployment:<br/>All 5 simultaneously<br/>= ~5 minutes<br/><br/>3x FASTER!]

        SEQ -.->|Improved by| PAR
    end

    style START fill:#34a853,color:#fff
    style PARALLEL fill:#fbbc04,color:#000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style UPDATE fill:#4285f4,color:#fff
    style ORCHESTRATOR fill:#4285f4,color:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style COMPLETE fill:#34a853,color:#fff
    style PAR fill:#34a853,color:#fff
    style SEQ fill:#ea4335,color:#fff
